OL,3,COmissions in care likely contributed
OL,4,Cto death of Sarah Adams, coroner rules
OL,6,FA woman from Reading took her own life
OL,7,Fafter being discharged from a
OL,8,Fspecialist mental hospital without a
OL,9,Fcare plan, an inquest has heard.
OL,11,FSarah Adams, who was described as a
OL,12,Ffun-loving lady, suffered from
OL,13,Fparanoid schizophrenia.
OL,15,FIn September 2021 her health began
OL,16,Fdeteriorating and when she was ill,
OL,17,FSarah spent a month under the care of
OL,18,Fthe mental health crisis team before
OL,19,Fbeing released into community care.
