OL,6,FLater, her health worsened again, and
OL,7,Fshe was admitted to the Cygnet Harrow
OL,8,FHospital after making an attempt on
OL,9,Fher life.
OL,11,FIt was issues relating to her
OL,12,Fdischarge from there that a coroner in
OL,13,FReading said most likely contributed
OL,14,Ftowards her death.
OL,16,FWhen she left the hospital, she was
OL,17,Fanxious about who would care for her.
OL,18,FShe left with a large amount of
OL,19,Fmedication and a visit that she was
OL,20,Fexpecting from the crisis care team
OL,21,Fdidn't materialise.
