OL,4,Cto death of Sarah Adams, coroner rules
OL,6,FThe coroner said it was likely that
OL,7,Fshe felt out of control and the
OL,8,Ffollowing day she was found dead.
OL,10,FThe coroner delivered a narrative
OL,11,Fconclusion finding that Sarah had
OL,12,Ftaken her own life, but the omissions
OL,13,Fin her care on discharge from Cygnet
OL,14,FHarrow Hospital have most likely
OL,15,Fcontributed to her death.
