OL,4,Cto death of Sarah Adams, coroner rules
OL,6,FSarah's niece, Izzy Adams, today told
OL,7,FITV Meridian what happened to her was
OL,8,Fheartbreaking and horrendous. She
OL,9,Fsaid: "It's heartbreaking. You know,
OL,10,Fanyone with, you know, mental illness,
OL,11,Fyou, you know it's not day by day,
OL,12,Fit's different.
OL,14,F"Every day is a different day. Um, and
OL,15,Fobviously when she's bad, the days
OL,16,Fwere horrendous, painful to see. You
OL,17,Fknow, someone suffering like that,
OL,18,Fit's just horrendous, and you don't
OL,19,Fwish it on anyone."
