OL,7,Fafter the inquest.
OL,9,FA Cygnet spokesperson said: "We would
OL,10,Flike to express our deepest
OL,11,Fcondolences to Sarah's family and all
OL,12,Fthose who continue to be affected by
OL,13,Fher loss.
OL,15,F"We take our responsibilities to
OL,16,Fprovide safe care extremely seriously.
OL,17,FWe always seek to ensure lessons
OL,18,Flearned are identified and shared, and
OL,19,Fwe are committed to working together
OL,20,Fwith other organisations and partners
OL,21,Facross mental health services.
