OL,6,F"Where areas for improvement have been
OL,7,Fidentified at Cygnet Hospital Harrow,
OL,8,Fwe have been working hard to address
OL,9,Fthem. For example, we have new
OL,10,Fleadership in place at the service,
OL,11,Fincluding a new hospital manager, who
OL,12,Fis overseeing positive changes. We
OL,13,Fhave strengthened governance processes
OL,14,Fat the hospital, reviewed elements of
OL,15,Four discharge policy, and increased
OL,16,Finvestment to renovate the ward
OL,17,Fenvironments and enhance service user
OL,18,Fexperience.
